snippet.title: canVERSE Trailer
snippet.description:
Play backgammon, checkers, and chess versus friends or computer AI with different difficulty levels. Local and online gameplay, with online support for 2 players and 62 spectators. All with voice chat.

Free Steam download | https://store.steampowered.com/app/1710720/canVERSE/
